{"tid":781345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水務署水質監測驗水結果　一處所一度驗出鎳超標3.1倍","createTime":"2018-08-15T23:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T10:05:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c1c83790476d47120817bd4a7f52364d5cdc5c7","tid":781345,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180814/large/1534240330_5cf2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180814%2Flarge%2F1534240330_5cf2.png&h=38c77050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「水質監測優化計劃」最新每周檢測結果，發現抽驗的其中一個處所在首輪檢測時驗出重金屬「鎳」超標3.1倍。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n自多條新落成的屋邨爆出食水含鉛量超標後，水務署去年底推出「水質監測優化計劃」，於全港食水帳戶隨機抽選處所化驗其食水中6種金屬含量，根據新一輪每周結果，水務署在其中一個處的第一級水樣本、即「日間隨機取樣」方法，驗出其含鎳量為每公升290微克，超出標準每公升70微克3.1倍。<br />\n<br />\n水務署稱，即時已按既定的兩級取樣規程，即抽取30分鐘靜水樣本作第二級，結果得出符合標準，認為相關處所的食水水質符合標準。署方稱，第一級水樣本出現超標，可能是因為收集水樣本之前，水龍頭靜水時間太長或偶然出現的金屬微粒引致。該處其餘5種金屬物的含量，包括鉛含量均未有驗出超標情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180814/58562844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58562844&d=nkxv9pFi4VjXiou7Gv4LbePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=b20f90cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F58562844&h=cccfa307\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180814/58562844</a>"},{"pid":"1d197078047c36bb32b69035589bacf48adab72c","tid":781345,"uid":119769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:51:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d3d5809671564a5e498562b0b9e352d57534894","tid":781345,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T00:24:27.000Z","msg":"沒事兒"},{"pid":"c0e1bf00d039110a4148e0439cb8f95d513b1abd","tid":781345,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{